channel.title: MooseScape Beta 50%!
channel.description:
Well i am 50% into the beta of my latest project MooseScape, I have been working on this with my team.
Current Credits - 20%% Wolf, 50%% me & 30% My Development team.
Latest updates 50%/V0.5 - Fully fixed barrages in wild no longer need 100+ to cast. - Better pk system. - Working economy now many ways to get money and nearly all skills (thanks to monkey) - agility (::agility) - thieving (ardy) - rune crafting - (few glitches and bugs) (commands ::runecraft) - woodcutting (cammy best place) - herblaw (fixed that u identify guam herbs to 3 then make attack pots) - fire making
left - cooking - fletching - slayer
My accomplishments in version 30%/V0.3 - Money from wcing (credz to whoever is helping :]) - Add npcs to every city - yayyyy - Fix food autotimer - Working ::starter command :] - Remove all shops and replace with my own custom - 50% - Remove summoning and replace with a few mobile shops in the music tab - Decided to leave and just fix (1 npc at a time) - Fix a few item glitches like new crystal bow and mud staff (so they dont hit uber fast) - Get more coders/testers :] - Fixed ::pnpc :] - Added my own version of whitewolf mountain and druid camp near fally - Fixed a few of the rapids - Made range a bit faster still too slow :S - Money Wcing Beta - Only works for normal trees atm. - Fixed mass wcing - sorta...
20%/V0.2 Accomplishments. - Fixed Whip and D scimmy spec no longer D/C's when equiped - 100% me - Fixed eating timer (originally took about 4 secs to eat and wouldnt eat in combat) now fully works - 50% Ownnage Plz 50% Pker - Fixed magic xp alching is no longer instant lvling but does give money - 50% me 50% wolf. - Added full edgy monastery and fixed wildy, added all the monks and everything. - Fixed the bows in wild no longer rapid hits, still havent fixed in duel arena :S - Removed a lot of the specs because they would lagg out and glitch up just doing emote not hitting - 70% me 30% My friend brian :] - Added ::home command to take you back to the monastary. - Monastery based (original idea of mine) 100% me. - Fixed about 60% of the glitched npcs like delrith, Removed over half of all D/C'ing npcs and re-replace most in correct Co-ords - 80% me - Solution to jad cave lagging out you can now you ::jad - Removed all commands using ::barrows ::lett etc, gives toolkit :P - 100% me - Umm sort of fixed the alching so it goes back to mage book (only works for superheat atm) - Full based npc training - 70% wolf for system 30% me for a lot of npcs :] - Removed over 50% of bankers to reduce lagg - Removed a few non working doors that disconnect - Thanks to i_own__u for making me webclient (under construction) - 100% i own u - Fixed the 1hp glitch on a few npcs such as the tzok's - Evened out the damage between Att/def & aggresive. - More to come!
Want to join the team? Register here http://z7.invisionfree.com/moosevill3/index.php?act=idx
Note that this is here for development purposes and it is under the Development/Help section so please don't flame. Don't say that this is advertising because i am not giving out the hamachi networks nor the custom port.
I would also like to give 5% of my credits to Simonkills1 for testing my server and helping me find glitches. And another 5% to Iron Skillz for being an awesome coder :]
